These stories were based in the

00:12:54.295 --> 00:12:57.285
Victorian slums, or poor areas of the

00:12:57.285 --> 00:12:59.855
city where many of the readers lived,

00:13:00.245 --> 00:13:02.645
and they turned the grim surroundings

00:13:02.645 --> 00:13:05.255
into adventurous sites of mystery.

