Do you think that the concerns

00:22:42.961 --> 00:22:44.831
about violent video games or

00:22:45.111 --> 00:22:47.081
films are any different to the

00:22:47.081 --> 00:22:48.931
concerns about Penny Dreadfuls?

00:22:49.591 --> 00:22:51.011
If so, why?

00:22:51.781 --> 00:22:53.661
I would love to know, so let’s

